author: Kuokka77
description:
Main theme from Atari STe demo "SaboTagE" (2016, Paradox) by 505.
Art "Dare To Be Yourself" by Vasyl/Joker^SWEET16, 2nd at Silly Venture 2024 SE Atari ST/E gfx compo.

French CA4003290 Atari STe with new Mean Well RPD-60A PSU (SidecarTridge.com variety). Playback using SND Player v1.51.

STe hardware has its issues and mine is not an exception. The infamous DAC whistle was removed using iZotope RX spectral de-noiser. DMA audio crackling, while not 100% eliminated, got improved dramatically after applying Exxos STE DAC CRACKLES POP FIX (additional grounding for U500 and U501 via bodge wires). STe also has very hot RCA outputs. Luckily RME Babyface Pro FS in professional +4 dBu recording reference level mode can take it without clipping.
title: Atari music: 505 - SaboTagE (STe🎧bx_)

author: Kuokka77
description:
"Uncensored parts 1 & 2" by Big Alec. Originals by Dane for C64.
Art from the Uncensored C64 demo.

French CA4003290 Atari STe with new Mean Well RPD-60A PSU (SidecarTridge.com variety).
Playback using SND Player v1.51.

STe hardware has its issues, mine is not an exception. The infamous DAC whistle was removed using iZotope RX 6 spectral de-noiser. Crackling during DMA audio playback, while not 100% eliminated, got improved dramatically after applying Exxos STE DAC CRACKLES POP FIX (additional grounding for U500 and U501 via bodge wires).
title: Atari music: Big Alec - Uncensored parts 1 & 2 (STe🎧bx_)
